quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,42,"Kasε: “Hwan na obetumi abͻ mo ho ban afri Ahummͻborͻ Hene no nsam wͻ anadwo ne adekyeε mu? Daabi, (obiara nnihͻ), nanso wͻ’dane wͻn ho fri wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn abodin ne Nenkaekaeε ho"
  21,43,Anaasε wͻn wͻ anyame a wͻ’bεbͻ wͻn ho ban afri Yεn hͻ? Wͻ’nni tumi a wͻ’de boa wͻn ho na kampεsε wͻ’abͻ wͻn ho ban afri Yεn (asotwee) mu
  21,44,"Daabi, Yε’bͻͻ woi nom ne wͻn agyanom akͻnhoma kͻpem sε nkwa (nna no) yεε (wͻn ani so) tenten maa wͻn. Enti (boniayεfoͻ no) nhunuu sε Yε’rete nsaase (a na wͻ’di so tumi no) so nkakrankakra firi ahyeε no soͻ? Enti wͻn na wͻ’bedi nkonim"
  21,45,"(Nkͻmhyεni), kasε: “Medeε Adiyisεm no na mede bͻ mo kͻkͻ, na ͻsosifoͻ no deε, sε yεbͻ no kͻkͻ mpo a ͻnnte frε no.“"
  21,46,"Ampa sε wo Wura Nyankopͻn asotwee no ho mframa sͻ wͻn mu a wͻ’bεka sε: “Adi ayε yεn. Nokorε sε na yεyε abͻneεfoͻ”"
  21,47,"Yε’de nokorε nsania no besi hͻ ama Wusͻreε da no, na yennsisi ͻkra biara ketekete koraa. Sε (ne dwuma pa anaa bͻne) mu duro tesε wisa aba mpo a Yε’de bεba (akontabuo mu). Na Yε’sombo wͻ akontabuo ho"
  21,48,"Nokorε sε Yεde Furqaan maa Mose ne Aaron, ne nhyerεnee ne afutusεm dema Nyame surofoͻ no"
  21,49,"Wͻn a wͻ’suro wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn wͻ nsumaeε mu no, wͻn na wͻ’bͻ hu wͻ Dͻnhwere no ho"
  21,50,Saa (Qur’aan) yi yε Afutusεm a nhyira wͻ mu a Y’asiane; enti mobεpo anaa